.TH ABRAFLEXI-MCP 1 "January 2026" "1.0.0" "AbraFlexi MCP Server Manual"
.SH NAME
abraflexi-mcp \- MCP server for AbraFlexi integration
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B abraflexi-mcp
[\fIoptions\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B abraflexi-mcp
is a Model Context Protocol (MCP) server that provides access to AbraFlexi accounting systems.
It uses the FastMCP framework to expose tools for managing invoices, contacts, products, and more.
.SH OPTIONS
The application is primarily configured via environment variables.
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_URL
URL of the AbraFlexi server (e.g., https://demo.flexibee.eu:5434).
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_COMPANY
Company identifier in AbraFlexi.
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_LOGIN
Username for authentication.
.TP
.B ABRAFLEXI_PASSWORD
Password for authentication.
.TP
.B READ_ONLY
Whether to enable read-only mode (default: true).
.SH TOOLS
The server provides various tools including:
.IP \(bu 2
\fBinvoice_issued_get\fR, \fBinvoice_issued_create\fR ...
.IP \(bu 2
\fBcontact_get\fR, \fBcontact_create\fR ...
.IP \(bu 2
\fBproduct_get\fR, \fBproduct_create\fR ...
.SH FILES
.TP
.I .env
Environment variable configuration file.
